channel.title: Advertising Question
channel.description: I'm trying to advertise my server on the site, CodeFasga. When I type in the IP, and I click submit, it says "An invalid IP address was entered". It is a Valid IP, I have the server running, and I have the IP in No-Ip checked, the face is blushing, etc... Yet, it still wont work. Any idea what's wrong?
